  "title": "Business Development Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong>:\nAs a Business Development Associate, you will support campaign expansion by engaging customers, supporting marketing efforts, and learning core sales and business skills.<br />\n<strong>Key Responsibilities</strong>:\nEngage potential customers and partners\nSupport campaign growth initiatives\nDevelop communication and negotiation skills\nAssist in team and business development activities<br />\n<strong>Requirements</strong>:\nGrowth-oriented mindset\nStrong interest in sales and marketing\nWillingness to learn and develop leadership skills<br />\n<strong>Opportunities</strong>:\nMentorship and coaching\nLeadership development pathway\nPerformance-based incentives</p>",
